{214}{}{为了在他思想的光辉中工作。此外，这很容易，因为亚伦有兴趣在他的旗帜下殖民这个社区。 -- For work in the glory of His ideas. Besides, it was easy, because Aaron is interested in colonizing the neighborhood under his banners.}
